content:
Standing before the open doors of a massive structure in the courtyard, you find Lunn once again. From his lap spills a haphazard tangle of cables, connectors, and other Estian bric-a-brac. Many cables lead to an exposed panel in the wall beside the open door. Lunn looks somewhat perplexed as he thoughtfully bites his thumbnail.

Clear Lunn with   to ask what he's doing.
